      <title>Changelog</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/fckeditor_transparent_integration/news/changelog</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
v 0.3.4:&lt;br /&gt;
 - Re-engineered upload mecanism in ezFckFileManager, now fixes a few&lt;br /&gt;
 issues with special rights given on editing sections as it uses&lt;br /&gt;
 ezpublish API to create objects.&lt;br /&gt;
 - Fix for view template&lt;br /&gt;
 v 0.3.3:&lt;br /&gt;
 - Fix for ereg regexp in autoload file. Escaping characters have been&lt;br /&gt;
 removed to keep compatibility with php&gt;=4.4.2 (Olivier&lt;br /&gt;
 Pierret)&lt;br /&gt;
 v 0.3.2:&lt;br /&gt;
 - Added ezFileManager to FCKEditor image insertion. This will allow&lt;br /&gt;
 user to add images and flash from the "media" section. It will be&lt;br /&gt;
 naturally browsed and objects will be added by their real url&lt;br /&gt;
 relative adress. Upload new images is also possible, contents will be&lt;br /&gt;
 automatically created. Warning: relative adresses imply possible&lt;br /&gt;
 moving sites problems with url mode (if site is handled in&lt;br /&gt;
 subdirectories).&lt;br /&gt;
 v 0.3.1:&lt;br /&gt;
 - Added per-class customization mecanism&lt;br /&gt;
 - Added support for editor's height (based on "optimal number of&lt;br /&gt;
 lines" attribute given in the objectClass)&lt;br /&gt;
 - Fix for is_empty bug after edition with FCK (Petr Mifek)&lt;br /&gt;
 v 0.3:&lt;br /&gt;
 - No more synchronisation system and hidden areas! Textfield is&lt;br /&gt;
 natively replaced with the fck instance. Thanks to&lt;br /&gt; SÃ©bastien Parizot for his ideas ;)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
